verses.text: When \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* went \w out|strong="H3318"\w* of \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*, the \w house|strong="H1004"\w* of \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* from a \w people|strong="H5971"\w* of strange \w language|strong="H3937"\w*;
\w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* was his \w sanctuary|strong="H6944"\w*, \add and\add* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* his \w dominion|strong="H4475"\w*.
The \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \add it\add*, and \w fled|strong="H5127"\w*: \w Jordan|strong="H3383"\w* was \w driven|strong="H5437"\w* \w back|strong="H0268"\w*.
The \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w* \w skipped|strong="H7540"\w* like \w rams|strong="H0352"\w*, \add and\add* the little \w hills|strong="H1389"\w* like \w lambs|strong="H1121"\w*.

What \add ailed\add* thee, O thou \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*, that thou \w fleddest|strong="H5127"\w*? thou \w Jordan|strong="H3383"\w*, \add that\add* thou wast \w driven|strong="H5437"\w* \w back|strong="H0268"\w*?
Ye \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w*, \add that\add* ye \w skipped|strong="H7540"\w* like \w rams|strong="H0352"\w*; \add and\add* ye little \w hills|strong="H1389"\w*, like \w lambs|strong="H1121"\w*?

\w Tremble|strong="H2342"\w*, thou \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*, at the \w presence|strong="H6440"\w* of the \w Lord|strong="H0113"\w*, at the \w presence|strong="H6440"\w* of the \w God|strong="H0433"\w* of \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*;

Which \w turned|strong="H2015"\w* the \w rock|strong="H6697"\w* \add into\add* a \w standing|strong="H0098"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w*, the \w flint|strong="H2496"\w* into a \w fountain|strong="H4599"\w* of \w waters|strong="H4325"\w*.
